Edit a Bucket Column
When itâ€™s time to add, remove, or change buckets in a bucket column, edit it.

REQUIRED EDITIONS AND USER PERMISSIONS
Available in: Salesforce Classic (not available in all orgs) and Lightning Experience
Available in: Enterprise, Performance, Unlimited, and Developer Editions

USER PERMISSIONS NEEDED
Enhanced Folder Sharing to add, edit, or delete a bucket column in private reports:
Create and Customize Reports
Enhanced Folder Sharing to add, edit, or delete a bucket column in public and private reports:

Edit the report.
Click | Edit Bucket Column in Lightning Experience.
In Salesforce Classic, click  and select Edit Bucket Field from the Fields pane under Bucket Fields.

Add, remove, or change buckets and bucket values.
Click Apply.
Click Save.
